articles.contents:
Indigo Bannister
          
          
            
              I am a second-year Master’s student at the Bren School of Environmental Science and Management at UC Santa Barbara studying conservation planning and the water quality impacts of fire.
              I love swing dancing (Lindy Hop), baking (sourdough anyone?), and all things outdoors.
